Mixed Table Inheritance
===

Mixted Table Inheritance(MTI) mitigates the drawbacks of Single Table Inheritance(STI). Providing an elegant solution for cases where many models have a lot of common fields and functionality, but their great number of unique fields make STI infeasible.


